{"type":"message","id":"4fd89bf7","parentId":"61ceb516","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:36:45.103Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The build succeeds without errors. All three widgets compile correctly. Let me provide a summary of what was accomplished.","thinkingSignature":"45b4760c8352e2a30dac10ce5b5cc02965fb8392ffabff8977fb775496f890f1"},{"type":"text","text":"Build succeeds with no errors. All three widgets are now fully integrated with the API.\n\n---\n\n**What was done:**\n\n**BillsWidget.tsx** — Complete rewrite of the data layer:\n- Added `useState<Bill[]>([])` and `useState<boolean>(true)` for loading, `useRef` for `hasLoaded`\n- `useEffect` (mount only) fetches `GET /api/bills` → extracts `data.bills`\n- `hasLoaded` ref ensures `loading=false` only after first successful fetch\n- Add bill: POST `/api/bills/action` with `action:\"add\"` + optimistic state update\n- Mark paid: POST with `action:\"markPaid\"` + state update\n- Delete: POST with `action:\"delete\"` + state update\n- Loading skeleton during fetch, Add Bill inline form\n\n**MoneyWidget.tsx** — Replaced localStorage-based approach with API:\n- Fixed all three wrong endpoint references (`/api/money/backup`) → correct `GET /api/money` and `POST /api/money/action`\n- Added loading state with `hasLoaded` ref\n- Add transaction: POST `action:\"add\"` with `{id, date, description, amount, type}`\n- Delete transaction in history modal: POST `action:\"delete\"`\n- Preserved all original UI: 3-account toggle, income/expense form, history modal, totals modal\n\n**HabitsWidget.tsx** — Rebuilt to match the actual API structure:\n- Original had hardcoded `water/stretch/vacuum/laundry/bedMade/meals` fields incompatible with the flexible `{id, name, color, completedDates[]}` API format\n- New UI shows habits as a list with color dots, today toggle (✓), add habit form with color picker, and history modal showing recent completion dates\n- Toggle: POST `/api/habits/action` with `action:\"toggle\", habit:{id}, date:\"2026-03-29\"` + optimistic update with revert on failure\n- Add: POST with `action:\"add\"` + new habit object\n- Delete: POST with `action:\"delete\"`\n\n**API verified working:** All three `GET` endpoints and `POST` actions tested successfully against `localhost:3001`."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":29597,"output":496,"cacheRead":16044,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46137,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774798591183,"responseId":"061879ff2171b3f5c05ded8ca5b648ba"}}
